      • handleMinMaxEndKey

        protected void handleMinMaxEndKey​(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent event)
                           throws java.lang.Exception
        On Min/Max TF Key Up, determines if an error message needs to display There was initially an error with this method where it was not removing the error if the conditions were fixed and corrected. This was changed by using validateInventory() rather than its own logic. Now both inventory event methods are handled the same way and clear the error message if the problem is solved.
        Parameters:
